     = Move all effects (state writes) before any calls to `.run()` to prevent reentrancy vulnerabilities.
Warning [WSAZ0374000]: Not all paths through the function run all Finals. 1/2 paths contain at least one Final that is never run.
    --> compiler-test:13:1
     |
  13 | final fn finalize_do_work(f: Final, a: u32) {
